description: Taking self-serve frozen yogurt on the go, Rhino's is really bringing your sweet tooth something special.Their years of experience in the frozen treat business is sure to show when they come to your event with the best yogurt, soft serve, sorbet, and gelato around. That's not even mentioning their friendly staff and great attitude. With their wide selection of flavors and toppings, this is easily the most unique and amazing self-serve experience in all of Ohio!
name: Rhino's Frozen Yogurt & Soft Serve
